        <!-- ========== FAQ SECTION ========== -->
        <section class="se-section">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-6 se-faq">
                        <h6 class="underline">How many people are there on the team?</h6>
                        <p>Right now our team is small, but we are looking to expand as we gain more users and add more tools to the suite. This helps us keep our prices low and ensure personal support.</p>
                    </div> <!-- end se-faq -->

                    <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-6 se-faq">
                        <h6 class="underline">What is our history?</h6>
                        <p>Our team has worked in User Experience for a couple years before realizing the need for cheaper, but quality UX tools. We decided to start creating them for UX professionals.</p>
                    </div> <!-- end se-faq -->

                    <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-6 se-faq">
                        <h6 class="underline">How did it start?</h6>
                        <p>It started when we realized that UX professionals need a better method of testing than pen and paper. We made traditional UX methodologies into modern-day tools for your use.</p>
                    </div> <!-- end se-faq -->

                    <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-6 se-faq">
                        <h6 class="underline">What are our achievements?</h6>
                        <p>We're proud to launch TreeTool for information architecure and are planning on launching more tools like it in the near future.</p>
                    </div> <!-- end se-faq -->
                </div> <!-- end row -->
            </div> <!-- end container -->
        </section>

